Job Description
We require Energetic candidates for our I.T Sales Department. The following characteristics are required by the applicant :- - Excellent communication skills including writing and speaking- Able to manage multiple projects at the same time- Excellent interpersonal skills both in person and by phone, with high professionalism.- At least one year experience with administrative management- Bachelor’s degree preferred but not required; significant work experience can substitute for the degree.- Ability to accomplish projects with very little or no supervision.- Confident, mature and professional- Self-motivated and able to work independently- Able to respond in timely manner- Deadline oriented with a good attention to detail- Maintain high levels of motivation throughout the position
